<quantity box="[756,848,1843,1869]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" pageId="74" pageNumber="75" unit="km" value="1900.0">1900km</quantity>
SE of the nearest record in southwest New 
<collectingRegion box="[1339,1428,1843,1869]" country="Mexico" name="Mexico" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">Mexico</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
